==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Foreseen
<hw>Fore*seen"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>conj.</pos>, or (strictly)
<pos>p. p.</pos> <def>Provided; in case that; on condition that.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>One manner of meat is most sure to every complexion,
<qex>foreseen</qex> that it be alway most commonly in conformity of
qualities, with the person that eateth.</q> <rj><qau>Sir T.
Elyot.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Foreseer</ent>⟦br⟧
